<i> I'm from Powell, Wyoming.</i>

00:39.331 --> 00:41.665
What's kept me hooked
about making knives--

00:41.709 --> 00:43.709
<i> I love the heat.</i>
<i> I love the hot metal.</i>

00:43.753 --> 00:45.252
I love the slag
flying everywhere.

00:45.296 --> 00:47.796
<i> It's like therapy.</i>

00:47.840 --> 00:49.298
<i> - My name's Walter Sorrells.</i>

00:49.341 --> 00:51.258
I'm 53 years old.

00:51.302 --> 00:53.010
I started out as a novelist.

00:53.054 --> 00:55.471
<i> I was writing a book</i>
<i> about a bladesmith,</i>

00:55.514 --> 00:57.139
so I took this little
teeny piece of steel,

00:57.183 --> 00:58.724
<i> smashed on it with a hammer,</i>

00:58.768 --> 01:00.642
and I've been doing it
ever since.

01:00.686 --> 01:04.354
<i> - My name is Joseph Collett.</i>
<i> I am 32 years old.</i>

