go buy a new one, so I made one.

01:13.199 --> 01:15.574
<i> - My name is Theo Nazz.</i>
<i> I'm from New York City,</i>

01:15.618 --> 01:17.701
<i> and I'm 26 years old.</i>

01:17.745 --> 01:20.662
I plan to win the competition
simply by having the most fun.

01:20.706 --> 01:23.040
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

01:23.084 --> 01:24.625
- Welcome to the Forge.

01:24.668 --> 01:26.460
You've been hand-selected
to demonstrate

01:26.504 --> 01:29.004
