[cheers and applause]

12:34.045 --> 12:36.838
[both laugh]

12:36.882 --> 12:40.258
- So Walter finally has the can
off of his Damascus billet,

12:40.302 --> 12:42.761
and it's good to see that.

12:42.804 --> 12:44.387
- Erich, he's done
all the spreading

12:44.431 --> 12:46.890
he's gonna get out of that
thin piece of metal.

12:46.933 --> 12:49.350
He needs to start shaping it.

12:49.394 --> 12:50.935
- [bleep]

12:50.979 --> 12:52.228
I think I'm going
to the welder, dude.

12:52.272 --> 12:53.605
- What's that?

12:53.648 --> 12:55.982
- I think I'm going
to the welder.

12:56.026 --> 12:59.277
<i> I'm choosing</i>
<i> to weld my insert in,</i>

