19:27.333 --> 19:30.960
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

19:34.465 --> 19:36.549
<i> [dramatic music]</i>

19:36.593 --> 19:40.219
Bladesmiths, the judges have
completed their deliberation,

19:40.263 --> 19:42.054
and they've made
a final decision.

19:42.098 --> 19:43.431
It's time for one of you...

19:43.474 --> 19:44.849
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

19:44.893 --> 19:48.936
To leave the Forge.

19:48.980 --> 19:52.148
Erich, your blade
did not make the cut.

19:52.192 --> 19:54.233
- Erich, we really appreciated

19:54.277 --> 19:56.819
how diligently you worked
on that piece

19:56.863 --> 19:58.905
to laminate the steel together.

19:58.948 --> 20:02.909
The problem is there's a lot
of places where it's not welded.

20:02.952 --> 20:06.495
Also we noticed some
micro-cracking on the surface,

20:06.539 --> 20:08.539
<i> and we don't know</i>
<i> how deep that goes,</i>

20:08.583 --> 20:10.041
and that's why
we're sending you home.

20:10.084 --> 20:11.500
- Understandable.

20:11.544 --> 20:13.169
- Erich, please surrender
your blade.

20:13.213 --> 20:16.339
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

20:16.382 --> 20:18.257
- It is what it is.
I put the best blade

20:18.301 --> 20:20.718
I could forward
given the time that I had.

20:20.762 --> 20:22.428
I've loved every second
of being here.

20:22.472 --> 20:24.555
I may not be
a "Forged in Fire" champion,

20:24.599 --> 20:27.016
but I am so blessed
to have been here.

20:27.060 --> 20:29.060
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

20:29.103 --> 20:31.520
- Bladesmiths, you've made it
to the second round.

20:31.564 --> 20:33.105
Good job.

