In this round,
you'll turn your blades

20:35.068 --> 20:37.610
into fully-functional weapons
by attaching handles to them

20:37.654 --> 20:40.112
using the range of materials
in our pantry.

20:40.156 --> 20:42.156
You will have three hours
in this round.

20:42.200 --> 20:43.866
Your finished blades
will be tested

20:43.910 --> 20:47.787
in a tatami mat slice
and bone marrow chop.

20:47.830 --> 20:50.122
But keep in mind,
once that time runs out

20:50.166 --> 20:51.874
and your weapons
have been tested,

20:51.918 --> 20:53.918
one of you will have
to surrender his weapon

20:53.962 --> 20:55.586
and leave the Forge.

20:55.630 --> 20:56.921
Good luck, bladesmiths.

20:56.965 --> 21:00.091
Your time starts...now.

21:00.134 --> 21:01.926
- And here it goes.

21:01.970 --> 21:03.427
<i> - I've got big plans</i>
