I don't know exactly
what I'm looking at.

22:27.472 --> 22:29.430
There's just
a lot of meat to go through.

22:29.474 --> 22:31.223
It's gonna be...
[sighs]

22:31.267 --> 22:32.641
interesting...

22:32.685 --> 22:34.477
to say the least.

22:34.520 --> 22:37.938
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

22:37.982 --> 22:41.609
- This is some kind
of stabilized burl wood.

22:41.652 --> 22:43.486
It looks really cool,

22:43.529 --> 22:46.864
so I'm going with cool today.

